Callisto 6 takes place in Los Angeles in the year 2120, where a world of cyberpunk is about to be broken by the emergence of superheroes. Powered by the Cypher System, this original RPG is crafted by Eric Campbell and Sam de Leve. Synapse is on the loose and the team must act quickly if they are to stop the speedster before he hurts anyone... including himself.
